{"username": "SallieKrawcheck", "name": "Sallie Krawcheck", "text": "It\u2019s where men make more money than women, simply for being men; and it\u2019s where that differential increases when people become parents \u2014 with men earning a \u201cdaddy bonus\u201d and women paying a \u201cmommy tax.\u201d", "lang": "en", "in_reply_to": "1587459501875249152", "is_quote_status": false, "retweeted_tweet": null, "possibly_sensitive": null, "favorited": false, "date": "Tue Nov 01 15:00:13 +0000 2022", "quote_count": 0, "reply_count": 1, "favorite_count": 5, "view_count": null, "view_count_state": "Enabled", "retweet_count": 0, "place": null, "is_translatable": false, "edits_remaining": "5", "has_card": false, "thumbnail_title": null, "urls": [], "hashtags": []}
