{"username": "SallieKrawcheck", "name": "Sallie Krawcheck", "text": "In the news recently: \n\nMan does the wrong thing, gets his business funded. In fact, record amounts of funding.\n\nWomen do the right thing, get punished. \n\nLet\u2019s unpack those double standards a bit, shall we? https://t.co/0y4tTk8VVz", "lang": "en", "in_reply_to": null, "is_quote_status": false, "retweeted_tweet": null, "possibly_sensitive": false, "favorited": false, "date": "Tue Aug 23 21:44:42 +0000 2022", "quote_count": 2, "reply_count": 0, "favorite_count": 23, "view_count": null, "view_count_state": "Enabled", "retweet_count": 10, "place": null, "is_translatable": false, "edits_remaining": "5", "has_card": true, "thumbnail_title": "Ellevest", "urls": [{"display_url": "ellevest.com/magazine/raisi\u2026", "expanded_url": "https://www.ellevest.com/magazine/raising-elle/double-standard-wework-finland-prime-minister", "url": "https://t.co/0y4tTk8VVz", "indices": [208, 231]}], "hashtags": []}
{"username": "SallieKrawcheck", "name": "Sallie Krawcheck", "text": "Remaining silent on reproductive rights isn't a bullet dodged for employers, but rather a cost postponed. Let me explain: \n\nThis summer, I was at a gathering in the weeks after the striking down of Roe v. Wade with a senior exec from one of the country\u2019s largest corporations. \ud83e\uddf5", "lang": "en", "in_reply_to": null, "is_quote_status": false, "retweeted_tweet": null, "possibly_sensitive": null, "favorited": false, "date": "Mon Oct 03 17:33:44 +0000 2022", "quote_count": 2, "reply_count": 1, "favorite_count": 18, "view_count": null, "view_count_state": "Enabled", "retweet_count": 8, "place": null, "is_translatable": false, "edits_remaining": "5", "has_card": false, "thumbnail_title": null, "urls": [], "hashtags": []}
{"username": "SallieKrawcheck", "name": "Sallie Krawcheck", "text": "When women are financially healthy, *everyone* is better off. And yet, by @Ellevest's measure, women\u2019s financial health is tracking at the lowest level of the past five years \u2014 worse even than it was during the depths of the pandemic. How do we know?\n\nWe did the research.", "lang": "en", "in_reply_to": null, "is_quote_status": false, "retweeted_tweet": null, "possibly_sensitive": null, "favorited": false, "date": "Thu Sep 22 13:11:59 +0000 2022", "quote_count": 1, "reply_count": 1, "favorite_count": 14, "view_count": null, "view_count_state": "Enabled", "retweet_count": 8, "place": null, "is_translatable": false, "edits_remaining": "5", "has_card": false, "thumbnail_title": null, "urls": [], "hashtags": []}
