{"username": "SallieKrawcheck", "name": "Sallie Krawcheck", "text": "Other ah-ha\u2019s? 62% of women we surveyed said one of their top financial concerns is climate change (more, even, than are worried about retirement planning or the stock market); and 53% said the reversal of Roe v. Wade is impacting their financial mindset. https://t.co/EYSC1d1J61", "lang": "en", "in_reply_to": "1572936756986802180", "is_quote_status": false, "retweeted_tweet": null, "possibly_sensitive": false, "favorited": false, "date": "Thu Sep 22 13:12:01 +0000 2022", "quote_count": 0, "reply_count": 1, "favorite_count": 10, "view_count": null, "view_count_state": "Enabled", "retweet_count": 4, "place": null, "is_translatable": false, "edits_remaining": "5", "has_card": true, "thumbnail_title": "Survey: Where Women Put Their Money | Ellevest", "urls": [{"display_url": "ellevest.com/magazine/disru\u2026", "expanded_url": "https://www.ellevest.com/magazine/disrupt-money/ellevest-financial-wellness-survey-2022", "url": "https://t.co/EYSC1d1J61", "indices": [256, 279]}], "hashtags": []}
{"username": "SallieKrawcheck", "name": "Sallie Krawcheck", "text": "The bad news: 43% of women are actively worrying about money at least once a day, and 59% stress about money more than once a week. In both instances, we\u2019re out-worrying men (36% and 55%, respectively). Plus, just 14% of women (vs 30% of men) feel prepared for a recession.", "lang": "en", "in_reply_to": "1572936752733753345", "is_quote_status": false, "retweeted_tweet": null, "possibly_sensitive": null, "favorited": false, "date": "Thu Sep 22 13:12:00 +0000 2022", "quote_count": 1, "reply_count": 1, "favorite_count": 6, "view_count": null, "view_count_state": "Enabled", "retweet_count": 3, "place": null, "is_translatable": false, "edits_remaining": "5", "has_card": false, "thumbnail_title": null, "urls": [], "hashtags": []}
