{"username": "SallieKrawcheck", "name": "Sallie Krawcheck", "text": "Women report that they want to work at companies whose values align with theirs: 44% of women say they'd look to leave an employer whose views on reproductive rights do not align with their own. \ud83d\udc4b\ud83c\udffc That goes for 56% of millennial women, 53% of Latinas, and 45% of Black women.", "lang": "en", "in_reply_to": "1576988892653555717", "is_quote_status": false, "retweeted_tweet": null, "possibly_sensitive": null, "favorited": false, "date": "Mon Oct 03 17:33:46 +0000 2022", "quote_count": 0, "reply_count": 1, "favorite_count": 7, "view_count": null, "view_count_state": "Enabled", "retweet_count": 4, "place": null, "is_translatable": false, "edits_remaining": "5", "has_card": false, "thumbnail_title": null, "urls": [], "hashtags": []}
{"username": "SallieKrawcheck", "name": "Sallie Krawcheck", "text": "What are we worrying about? Women said their top-ranked $$ priority is supporting family, a category that includes family planning, child care, taking care of parents, etc. Men ranked growing retirement savings as their #1 financial priority.\u201d (Family came in fourth for men. \ud83d\ude12)", "lang": "en", "in_reply_to": "1572936754512154632", "is_quote_status": false, "retweeted_tweet": null, "possibly_sensitive": null, "favorited": false, "date": "Thu Sep 22 13:12:00 +0000 2022", "quote_count": 1, "reply_count": 1, "favorite_count": 7, "view_count": null, "view_count_state": "Enabled", "retweet_count": 2, "place": null, "is_translatable": false, "edits_remaining": "5", "has_card": false, "thumbnail_title": null, "urls": [], "hashtags": []}
{"username": "SallieKrawcheck", "name": "Sallie Krawcheck", "text": "Introducing the Ellevest Women\u2019s Financial Health Index, the first-ever comprehensive measure of women's financial health, and the Ellevest Financial Wellness Survey 2022, which dives into how women are thinking about \ud83d\udcb8 (and what they're doing with it). https://t.co/Jp3PMYvWlB", "lang": "en", "in_reply_to": "1572936749298614272", "is_quote_status": false, "retweeted_tweet": null, "possibly_sensitive": false, "favorited": false, "date": "Thu Sep 22 13:11:59 +0000 2022", "quote_count": 2, "reply_count": 1, "favorite_count": 4, "view_count": null, "view_count_state": "Enabled", "retweet_count": 1, "place": null, "is_translatable": false, "edits_remaining": "5", "has_card": false, "thumbnail_title": null, "urls": [{"display_url": "s3.amazonaws.com/production.ass\u2026", "expanded_url": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/production.assets.ellevest.com/documents/Ellevest-The-State-of-Womens-Financial-Wellness-in-2022.pdf", "url": "https://t.co/Jp3PMYvWlB", "indices": [254, 277]}], "hashtags": []}
{"username": "SallieKrawcheck", "name": "Sallie Krawcheck", "text": "We did it because it\u2019s difficult to change what you can\u2019t measure. While what we learned was grim, there were still data points that gave me hope. But make no mistake, it underscores how far we still have to go in achieving true financial gender equality. https://t.co/o4OluOVFxE", "lang": "en", "in_reply_to": "1572936750871486465", "is_quote_status": false, "retweeted_tweet": null, "possibly_sensitive": false, "favorited": false, "date": "Thu Sep 22 13:12:00 +0000 2022", "quote_count": 0, "reply_count": 1, "favorite_count": 4, "view_count": null, "view_count_state": "Enabled", "retweet_count": 1, "place": null, "is_translatable": false, "edits_remaining": "5", "has_card": true, "thumbnail_title": "The Ellevest Women\u2019s Financial Health Index | Ellevest", "urls": [{"display_url": "ellevest.com/magazine/disru\u2026", "expanded_url": "https://www.ellevest.com/magazine/disrupt-money/financial-health-index", "url": "https://t.co/o4OluOVFxE", "indices": [256, 279]}], "hashtags": []}
{"username": "SallieKrawcheck", "name": "Sallie Krawcheck", "text": "Crisis averted. Sigh of relief. Except maybe not. \n\n@Ellevest recently shared the results of our second annual Ellevest Financial Wellness Survey \u2014 and the truth is, silence can cost you women employees.\nhttps://t.co/EYSC1d2gVz", "lang": "en", "in_reply_to": "1576988891248087040", "is_quote_status": false, "retweeted_tweet": null, "possibly_sensitive": false, "favorited": false, "date": "Mon Oct 03 17:33:45 +0000 2022", "quote_count": 0, "reply_count": 1, "favorite_count": 5, "view_count": null, "view_count_state": "Enabled", "retweet_count": 2, "place": null, "is_translatable": false, "edits_remaining": "5", "has_card": true, "thumbnail_title": "Survey: Where Women Put Their Money | Ellevest", "urls": [{"display_url": "ellevest.com/magazine/disru\u2026", "expanded_url": "https://www.ellevest.com/magazine/disrupt-money/ellevest-financial-wellness-survey-2022", "url": "https://t.co/EYSC1d2gVz", "indices": [204, 227]}], "hashtags": []}
{"username": "SallieKrawcheck", "name": "Sallie Krawcheck", "text": "How are women reacting to this rapidly shifting landscape? They\u2019re sending their resumes out. That\u2019s right: A full 55% are looking for a new job. And 38% report that they are saving money so they can leave their job.\n\nWomen can\u2019t afford to stay where they don\u2019t have support. \ud83e\udd37\ud83c\udffc\u200d\u2640\ufe0f", "lang": "en", "in_reply_to": "1576988894079635461", "is_quote_status": false, "retweeted_tweet": null, "possibly_sensitive": null, "favorited": false, "date": "Mon Oct 03 17:33:46 +0000 2022", "quote_count": 0, "reply_count": 1, "favorite_count": 7, "view_count": null, "view_count_state": "Enabled", "retweet_count": 2, "place": null, "is_translatable": false, "edits_remaining": "5", "has_card": false, "thumbnail_title": null, "urls": [], "hashtags": []}
{"username": "SallieKrawcheck", "name": "Sallie Krawcheck", "text": "It\u2019s essential that we work to create opportunities for women to take action to build their best financial futures. And one of the first steps to driving real change is knowing where we\u2019re starting from. Read our annotated press release here: https://t.co/7ML8GgAvWf", "lang": "en", "in_reply_to": "1572936758483980288", "is_quote_status": false, "retweeted_tweet": null, "possibly_sensitive": false, "favorited": false, "date": "Thu Sep 22 13:12:01 +0000 2022", "quote_count": 0, "reply_count": 0, "favorite_count": 2, "view_count": null, "view_count_state": "Enabled", "retweet_count": 2, "place": null, "is_translatable": false, "edits_remaining": "5", "has_card": true, "thumbnail_title": "Ellevest", "urls": [{"display_url": "ellevest.com/magazine/news/\u2026", "expanded_url": "https://www.ellevest.com/magazine/news/financial-health-index-wellness-survey-annotated-press-release", "url": "https://t.co/7ML8GgAvWf", "indices": [243, 266]}], "hashtags": []}
{"username": "SallieKrawcheck", "name": "Sallie Krawcheck", "text": "Remote-first can come with allllllll of the potential interruptions that working from home can serve up. Curious, what\u2019s your top distraction?", "lang": "en", "in_reply_to": "1572192585439125509", "is_quote_status": false, "retweeted_tweet": null, "possibly_sensitive": null, "favorited": false, "date": "Tue Sep 20 19:50:51 +0000 2022", "quote_count": 0, "reply_count": 3, "favorite_count": 1, "view_count": null, "view_count_state": "Enabled", "retweet_count": 1, "place": null, "is_translatable": false, "edits_remaining": "5", "has_card": true, "thumbnail_title": null, "urls": [], "hashtags": []}
{"username": "SallieKrawcheck", "name": "Sallie Krawcheck", "text": "The good news: Women are 3x as likely to see financial wellness as critical to their overall well-being compared to 2021. And despite the turbulent year for the markets, 75% of women who invest for retirement did *not* pause their contributions. (\u2764\ufe0f to hear that at @Ellevest.)", "lang": "en", "in_reply_to": "1572936755816308736", "is_quote_status": false, "retweeted_tweet": null, "possibly_sensitive": null, "favorited": false, "date": "Thu Sep 22 13:12:01 +0000 2022", "quote_count": 0, "reply_count": 1, "favorite_count": 8, "view_count": null, "view_count_state": "Enabled", "retweet_count": 1, "place": null, "is_translatable": false, "edits_remaining": "5", "has_card": false, "thumbnail_title": null, "urls": [], "hashtags": []}
